---
title: Double Balsamic-Glazed Beef Rump with Orange & Green Bean Salad
description: Elevate your dinner game with this superquick gourmet meal! Juicy, tender beef is perfectly caramelised in a tangy-sweet balsamic glaze, then paired with a refreshing orange and green beans salad that’s bursting with citrusy crunch. It’s a bold and balanced dish that’s equal parts fancy and fun—sure to impress your taste buds!

